query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!"
            FROM transactions t
            WHERE t.user_id = $3 
              AND t.deleted_at IS NULL
              AND ($1::timestamptz IS NULL OR t.occurred_at >= $1)
              AND ($2::timestamptz IS NULL OR t.occurred_at <= $2)
              AND ($4::uuid IS NULL OR t.pocket_id = $4)
